        \stopnarrow

        \startnarrow
          {\em Pixel Racer}: A racing game.
        \stopnarrow

        \startnarrow
          {\em Tapeworm}: I'll skip the description for this one.
        \stopnarrow

        I would create and publish similar ads for each game and, a few weeks
        later (that's how long it took in the pre-internet days), I would be
        able to compare the results:

        \startplacetable
          \startxtable
            \startxtablehead[head]
              \startxrow
                \startxcell
                  Game
                \stopxcell
                \startxcell
